snippet.title: AMBER HEARD SPEAKS UP! WANTS NOTHING FROM DEPP?! (Parody)
snippet.description:
Hi guys thanks so much for tuning in, 
My name is Carla Yang, and Welcome to my channel!

I hope that you guys are having a wonderful day! and I wish you all Merry Christmas! and the happiest of Holidays!

This video is an Amber Heard Parody created for entertainment purposes only!

References used for this video, feel free to check them out:
MAIN INTERVIEW 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hBH5O1ukpq8&t=136s

AH Alleged drug use
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A7hCC1PNYt4&list=PL3b067p5TTpNZHhd3zAdy1I3Esjp8zu6p&index=31&t=62s

RECORDINGS
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cg9SvQSMnoE&list=PL3b067p5TTpNZHhd3zAdy1I3Esjp8zu6p&index=55&t=445s

https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/celebrities/2021/07/30/johnny-depp-granted-request-aclu-confirm-amber-heard-donation/5438287001/

https://radaronline.com/photos/a-penthouse-a-range-rover-125k-ambers-divorce-demands-revealed/


Disclaimer: All information used here is alleged, and used for entertainment purposes, as well as to give a personal opinion on the matter without claiming that is the truth. 

With that said I really hope you like this video, and if you do, don’t forget to give it a thumbs up and if you’re new, welcome aboard and feel free to subscribe if you'd like to! 
And please let me know what your thoughts are on this parody, I really appreciate all of your comments!

#amberheard #justiceforjohnnydepp #metoo
Thanks for watching! I really appreciate it, and stay tuned for more!
Please take care of yourselves and each other,  my name is Carla yang! and I will see you soon!
